Visual Studio 2010 Pro Language Pack pre-requisites:
  • Visual Studio 2010 Professional
  • .NET Framework 4 Language Pack

Installation Instructions

  1. It is necessary to install the English version of Visual Studio 2010 Professional before installing the Language Packs.
  2. Visual Studio 2010 Language Packs do not include .NET Framework 4 Language Packs. The .NET Framework 4 Language Packs need to be installed separately.
  3. Install the Visual Studio 2010 Professional Language Packs by running:
    1. vs_prolp.exe (Visual Studio IDE Language Pack (x86 & x64))
    2. HelpSetupLP_x86_lang.exe (Microsoft Help Viewer 1.0 Language Pack (x86)) or HelpSetupLP_x64_lang.exe (Microsoft Help Viewer 1.0 Language Pack (x64))

Files.Description: Visual Studio 2010 Lab Management Deployment Guide (x86) - (English)

Files.Notes:
Visual Studio 2010 Pro Language Pack pre-requisites:
  • Visual Studio 2010 Professional
  • .NET Framework 4 Language Pack

Installation Instructions

  1. It is necessary to install the English version of Visual Studio 2010 Professional before installing the Language Packs.
  2. Visual Studio 2010 Language Packs do not include .NET Framework 4 Language Packs. The .NET Framework 4 Language Packs need to be installed separately.
  3. Install the Visual Studio 2010 Professional Language Packs by running:
    1. vs_prolp.exe (Visual Studio IDE Language Pack (x86 & x64))
    2. HelpSetupLP_x86_lang.exe (Microsoft Help Viewer 1.0 Language Pack (x86)) or HelpSetupLP_x64_lang.exe (Microsoft Help Viewer 1.0 Language Pack (x64))
